installCommand: export PATH="/bin:$PATH" && curl https://static.lamdera.com/bin/linux/lamdera-1.1.0-linux-arm64 -o /usr/local/bin/lamdera && chmod a+x /usr/local/bin/lamdera && npm install
buildCommand: npx elm-pages gen && cd elm-stuff/elm-pages/ && lamdera make .elm-pages/Main.elm --output /dev/null
